data.description: Built in 2016. This home features 5 bedroom 3.5 bath. Open concept, owner's suite on the main floor.   Main floor owner suite features porcelain floors and the bathroom has a sauna that was installed last year. Open concept kitchen with newer appliances, quartz island, granite counter tops, pantry and plenty of cabinet space. The main floor is equipped with built in speakers in owner suite, living room and kitchen. Upstairs features a mini loft and 4 additional bedrooms with one room has its own bathroom. New roof will be replace soon.
